               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     An unsigned and undated copy of the <title>Mas̲navī-i Ma‘navī</title> (Spiritual Couplets) by <persName ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/98930150" key="person_98930150">Jalāl al-Dīn Rūmī
                        (1207–1273)</persName>, likely completed in <date cert="medium" notBefore="1700" notAfter="1800">18th-century</date> <placeName>India</placeName>. Some, but not all books open with brief, anonymous Persian prefaces.
                  </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_926-item1">
                     <author ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/98930150" key="person_98930150">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Jalāl al-Dīn Rūmī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">جلال الدین رومی</persName>
                     </author>
                     <editor role="scr"><persName role="scr">Ni‘mat Khān</persName> <foreign>نعمت خان</foreign></editor>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_20506" change="#ids-cleanup">Mas̲navī</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_20506" change="#ids-cleanup">مثنوی</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar" type="beginning"><locus from="1b" to="1b">برگ ۱پ (folio 1b):
                     </locus>  بشنو از نی چون حکایت میکند * و ز جدأیها شکایت  میکند.</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa"><locus from="281a" to="281b"> برگ ۲۸۱پ (folio 281a):</locus>
                        زء جان آسمانست این کلام * هر که ازین بر رود آید.                     </explicit>
                     <colophon xml:lang="fa"><locus from="281a" to="281b"> برگ ۲۸۱پ (folio 281a):</locus>
                        تمت تمام شد کارم نظام شد دفتر ششم من کلام مثنوی مولوی روم قدس الله.
                     </colophon>
                     <colophon>Colophon on <locus from="281a" to="281b">folio 281a</locus> unsigned and undated.</colophon>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                     <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_926-item1-item1">
